ou have to be able to see the MT and the mob. I had trouble doing this being so short and I wonder how hard it would be for the assist crowd to visually track a shorty MT in the same circumstances? <br><br>It just seems that height would really be advantageous especially while MT'ing. I also wonder if you large types can plow through the support crowd to taunt off the add mob killing the casters, I know I can't as a shortie.<br><br>If the peeps were sitting along the zone I couldn't run behind them but sometimes I could run and jump on/over their heads, hahhahaha but this wasn't reliable although it was fun!<br><br>So if you MT's would please post a few comment I'd appreciate it.<br><br>Thanks, Thoro <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ueqin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>eqin</A> at: 6/15/02 2:09:37 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubaadan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Baadan</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.magelo.com/res/eq/itemicon/0011.png" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 106<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/15/02 12:59:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1673.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How can us shorties MT effectively?</span><hr size=1> OMG that is the funniest thing I've ever seen!!<br><br>Here's your solution:<br><br>I'm not sure what level the spell is, but some time or another, 50+, SHAMAN get a spell that makes you bigger, pretty much the opposite of shrink.<br><br>As I half elf I grew to barbarian size. (medium sized ppl can only be shrunk or grown 1 size)<br><br>Large people can be shrunk two sizes and small people can be grown two sizes.<br><br><br>EDIT: Hmm I just looked on Casters Realm and I